      <tr>
        <td width="500" height="18" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#993333" class="box_titles">Farm farm farm .... <span class="box_titles_small">February 07, 2005, 02:15:57 PM by <a href="mailto:noah@uberyou.com">Noah</a></span>		</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		As you can see the site is back up and in full action again.  All you fanbois can relax now and feel free to hit the website 47 times an hour hoping to see some uber loot update.  This update will make even your bookmarked pornsites seem boring.  Lets start off with the tweaks made from the big patch.<br /><br /><B>Armor Tints</B> - Red storm trooper, clamshell, then black.  Im in favor of just having a /random for the color and look of your armor at this point. Rating: 4<br /><br /><B>HOs</B> - Ahh yes, hos.  Now made practically retard free!  The new animations are a bit rough on the system, but everyone loves playing on Atari mode anyways (hugs Nvidia)  Rating: 9<br /><br /><B>Armor Class</B> - Hurray for big numbers.  Numbers make me happy.  Bigger numbers are the uberer I r.  Rating: 9<br /><br /><B>New Heritages</B> - GEBs and Tranix.  If you love Lavastorm (yay trains and lava ports!!) then enjoy lagtastic hours of running everywhere in this zone.  Lets not forget you need to know 12 different languages (including Chinese and Spanish) to even get half way done.  Rating: 6<br /><br /><B>Metal Chests</B> - Wooden box with 2 41st lvl adept dropped from a groupx4 epic mob after spending 40 mins beating on 100 million hps... awesome way to spend friday night.  Now with the adjusted loot on these mobs, we have something to look forward to dragging 24 people to the depths of Sol Ro.  Thank you for this adjustment.  Rating: 8<br /><br /><B>Venekor</B> - Saved the best one for last.  Yes, the uber creation of Moorgard.  Before the tweek it was a good fight.  Challenging and some strat needed for success.  Someone felt it necessary to change this encounter from exciting to absurd.  If you are going to make some AE raid wide, think about putting in resist checks, toning down the 4k per tick dot, or make it have a managable range. I am sure your testers did great against him before you released it to the Live servers (/hug).  Rating: 2<br /><br />With all the glorious changes we have enjoying farming the metal boxes from x2 and x4 mobs.  Even though they made mobs hit harder (Hi2u 6k nukes)... Agi boost work for crap... these fellas just cowboy up and get it done.  Heres the spoils of their hard work.<br /><br /><table border=0 cellspacing=2 cellpadding=2 class="box_links"><tr><td valign="bottom"><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Sharlian Maul.JPG"></td><td valign="bottom"><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Idol of Focus.JPG"></td></tr><td>Grats Pathogenn!</td><td>Grats Mystique!</td></tr></table><br /><br /><br /><table border=0 cellspacing=2 cellpadding=2 class="box_links"><tr><td valign="bottom"><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Gloves of Madness.JPG"></td><td valign="bottom"><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Girdle of the Overloard.JPG"></td></tr><td>Grats Insognito!</td><td>Grats Endalmir!</td></tr></table><br /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Rathine Leafblade.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br />Grats Poyzin!
		<p>  :: <a href="/eq2/index.php?action=fullnews&amp;showcomments=1&amp;id=6">Comments (0)</a> ::  
