        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		So a couple days ago we talked to Nagafen, and I guess that after 500 years of being cooped up in the bottom of Solusek he's ready to get some booty.  He sent us to the crypt in Permafrost to get Vox all ready for him, but she wasn't in a particularly cooperative mood.  Common decency reared it's ugly head yet again, and we killed the insolent bitch.<br /><br />Noah was kind enough to provide this image.<br /><br /><center><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/spirit%20of%20vox.JPG"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/spirit%20of%20vox.JPG border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br />It took me 2 days to get around to making this update, but I was working on the site.
